    • 方法详细资料

      • encode

        void encode(IOSession session,
            java.lang.Object message,
            IProtocolOutput out)
     throws java.lang.Exception
        Encode higher-level message into binary or protocol-specific data. Invoked before a message fired to write to the remote endpoint
        参数:
        session - The current Session
        message - the message to encode
        out - The IProtocolOutput that will receive the encoded message
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - if the message violated protocol specification

      • dispose

        void dispose(IOSession session)
      throws java.lang.Exception
        Releases all resources related with this encoder.
        参数:
        session - The current Session
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - if failed to dispose all resources
